title: Aangan Indian Restaurant
typeOfFood: Lacto, Indian, Delivery, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Indian restaurant with vegetarian menu where several items can be prepared vegan including dal tadka, baigan bhartha, gobi, along with pea pulao rice and breads. Must specify vegan when ordering so curries and breads can be prepared with vegetable oil instead of ghee.
